'From Squeak5.3 of 28 May 2021 [latest update: #19459] on 6 November 2021 at 10:42:08 pm'!"Change Set:		MenuMorph-addAllFromFixDate:			6 November 2021Author:			Masashi UmezawaMenuMorph>>addAllFrom: should set default target to each menu items if they do not have their own targets.By this patch, Mantis bug:0005297 can be solved."!!MenuMorph methodsFor: 'construction' stamp: 'mu 11/6/2021 22:39'!addAllFrom: aMenuMorph 	aMenuMorph submorphs		do: [:each | 			(each isKindOf: MenuItemMorph)				ifTrue: [self						add: each contents						target: (each target ifNil: [self defaultTarget])						selector: each selector						argumentList: each arguments].			(each knownName = #line)				ifTrue: [self addLine]] ! !